# %% [markdown]
# # 🏥 Clinical MoE OCR Pipeline v2.0 — Kaggle T4×2 Edition
#
# **Production-grade Mixture-of-Experts OCR pipeline** for clinical document
# text extraction. Implements a 6-stage pipeline grounded in a 32-paper
# research corpus [P1]–[P32].
#
# ## Pipeline Architecture
# ```
# INPUT (PDF/Image)
#   → Stage 0: Pre-processing + Quality Scoring  [P1][P3][P4][P5]
#   → Stage 1: Layout Detection + Region Segmentation  [P6][P7][P15]
#   → Stage 2: Per-Region Quality + Routing Vector  [P1][P2]
#   → Stage 3: MoE Router (Rule-based Dynamic Routing)  [P26][P27]
#   → Stage 4: Expert Pool Execution  [P8]–[P14][P17]
#   → Stage 5: Post-OCR Correction + Provenance  [P23][P24]
# OUTPUT: Clean UTF-8 text + JSON provenance manifest
# ```
#
# ## Expert Pool (Dual T4 Assignment)
# | Expert | Model | Role | Device |
# |--------|-------|------|--------|
# | **A** | TrOCR-large [P8] | Handwriting (primary) | cuda:0 |
# | **A-Lite** | CRNN-CTC [P22] | Handwriting (fast) | stub |
# | **B** | PaddleOCR PP-OCRv4 [P9] | Printed text (default) | CPU |
# | **C** | DocTR [P10] | Structured form fallback | CPU |
# | **D** | GOT-OCR 2.0 [P11] | Complex / mixed content | cuda:1 |
# | **E** | Qwen2-VL-2B [P13] | Premium fallback | cuda:1 |
# | **F** | MIRAGE [P14] | Indian mixed-script | stub |
# | **G** | Donut [P17] | OCR-free templated forms | cuda:0 |
#
# ## Hardware: Kaggle T4×2 (2× 16 GB = 32 GB total VRAM)
# All experts **co-resident** — zero load/evict overhead.

